{"Sid":0,"Did":118126,"Id":"282273","Title":"礁溪成功新村聚落","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/d956cf5c-b453-495f-ad68-d856b5d806ac/108-her-pa-1808-201910252224125db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/a6e7a105-4777-4566-bef8-30db4159c94b/108-her-pa-1808-201910252224125db2e16a5063c1.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n礁溪成功新村居民當初是由來自下大陳的146戶526人所組成，由營造相關專業人員負責砌磚，大陳居民則負責攪拌水泥、搬運材料、挑磚等工作。成功新村在1956年7月落成，居民於7月29日與8月1日分兩批進住。 　　礁溪成功新村房舍共有三種規格：四口之家住在3.5坪的一層平房中，有109間；六口之家住在6坪的一層平房，有29間；七口之家則住在近7坪的一層平房，有8間。整個礁溪成功新村共有146間房舍。 　　除了住家房舍外，尚設置了許多公共空間或設施。公共空間包括：大禮堂，或稱「公房」，後因火災燒毀，於1993年改建為「武聖廟」；工廠，約750坪，曾製造過鞭炮、草繩袋、啤酒木箱、藤椅、衣架、糖果、紙捲軸、陀螺、書架與填充玩具，現已廢棄拆除成為空地。公共設施包括：飲用水井、溫泉水井、公共廁所（5座）等。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7696964","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8214206","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/BA414EA8-D4C8-4C8A-8024-ECFAC996B924","Original_Identifier":"282273","Keyword_Subject_1":"空間、地域與遷徙","alias":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 成功新村 / 聚落 / 礁溪","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:10:11","timelines":"","place":"礁溪鄉成功新村","address":"宜蘭縣礁溪鄉成功新村","longitude":"121.7696964","latitude":"24.8214206","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/da78aca1-9f5b-48e0-9146-185e5046e713/108-her-pa-1808-re-201910252226365db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/e1018b4c-3b7f-4fab-b3b0-